Source: hifiberryos-meta
Section: metapackages
Priority: optional
Maintainer: HiFiBerry <support@hifiberry.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13)
Standards-Version: 4.6.0
Homepage: https://hifiberry.com/os

Package: hbos-test
Architecture: all
Depends: hifiberry-baseconfig,
         hifiberry-configurator,
         hifiberry-eeprom,
         hifiberry-testtools,
         hifiberry-webui
Description: HiFiBerry OS testing meta-package
 This meta-package provides the minimal HiFiBerry OS components plus
 testing and development tools. It includes:
 .
  - Base system configuration (hifiberry-baseconfig)
  - Web-based configuration interface (hifiberry-configurator)
  - HAT EEPROM tools and utilities (hifiberry-eeprom)
  - Modern web interface (hifiberry-webui)
  - Testing tools and utilities (hifiberry-testtools)
 .
 This package is ideal for development, testing, and quality assurance
 environments where diagnostic and debugging capabilities are needed.

Package: hbos-minimal
Architecture: all
Depends: hifiberry-baseconfig,
         hifiberry-configurator,
         hifiberry-eeprom,
         hifiberry-dsp,
         hifiberry-mpd,
         hifiberry-audiocontrol,
         hifiberry-pipewire,
         hifiberry-webui
Description: HiFiBerry OS minimal meta-package
 This meta-package provides the minimal set of HiFiBerry OS components
 required for basic functionality. It includes:
 .
  - Base system configuration and hardware detection (hifiberry-baseconfig)
  - Web-based configuration interface (hifiberry-configurator)
  - HAT EEPROM tools and utilities (hifiberry-eeprom)
  - DSP toolkit for audio processing (hifiberry-dsp)
  - Music Player Daemon (hifiberry-mpd)
  - Audio control utilities (hifiberry-audiocontrol)
  - PipeWire audio server (hifiberry-pipewire)
  - Modern web interface (hifiberry-webui)
 .
 This package is ideal for users who want a lightweight installation with
 essential audio functionality and web-based management.

Package: hbos-full
Architecture: all
Depends: hifiberry-baseconfig,
         hifiberry-audiocontrol,
         hifiberry-configurator,
         hifiberry-eeprom,
         hifiberry-dsp,
         hifiberry-librespot,
         hifiberry-mpd,
         hifiberry-pipewire,
         hifiberry-raat,
         hifiberry-shairport,
         hifiberry-squeezelite,
         hifiberry-webui
Description: HiFiBerry OS full meta-package
 This meta-package provides the complete set of HiFiBerry OS components
 for full functionality. It includes all audio streaming services and
 advanced features:
 .
  - All components from hbos-minimal
  - Spotify Connect support (hifiberry-librespot)
  - AirPlay streaming (hifiberry-shairport)
  - Squeezebox/Logitech Media Server support (hifiberry-squeezelite)
  - RAAT streaming for Roon integration (hifiberry-raat)
 .
 This package provides the complete HiFiBerry OS experience with all
 streaming services, advanced audio processing, and development tools
 for a comprehensive audio streaming and management environment.
